               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> I suppose you had no money transaction of any kind with him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I had no public transaction.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185802220054"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
