               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> They have sent in their accounts, I suppose? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, they have not—I have drawn all my pay.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
