                  </hi>. I was in the regiment from June, 1855, until it was disembodied. I received my pay from Cocks and Co.—I received no pay from the prisoner, only allowances and contingent money.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18580222-name-252" type="witnessName">
